{"tid":1622700,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Pixel 4 竟支援雙曝光設定？超靚實拍照片大量流出","createTime":"2019-10-04T16:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:30:53.000Z","uid":141060,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67aeb534b87173b16c3820a1735261f01c182d16","tid":1622700,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3368015/org/286287da44086f43c819047dc8c0dfaf.jpeg/LqCM-AcsalUWdarUH3BxDk3u6upiWmSNC5E2LAuRNiw?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3368015%2Forg%2F286287da44086f43c819047dc8c0dfaf.jpeg%2FLqCM-AcsalUWdarUH3BxDk3u6upiWmSNC5E2LAuRNiw%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=701bf2b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle 即將在 10 月 15 日發表他們的「親生」Android 新機 Pixel 4 系列，雖然到現在這個系列都未有跡象會在香港推出，但每代的獨門技術總令人驚喜。<br />\n<br />\n而來到今代 Pixel 4 及 Pixel 4 XL，早有傳聞指出 Google 將會加入超強的拍攝能力，除了之前的「星星」拍攝模式之外，稍早前又有宣傳片以及實機拍攝照片流出，顯示新機將會支援 Dual Exposure 雙重曝光設定，讓用家可以拍出更合乎心目中效果的相片。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的雙重曝光，亦即類似人手 HDR 設定，可以在拍攝相片前自行設定相片中的陰影及亮部的強度，透過兩者曝光時間不同，合成一張符合用家想要效果的相片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在網上就流出了 Pixel 4 的宣傳，當中出現了 Dual Exposure 的操作方法，以兩個滑桿就可以增減陰影及亮部強度，這種設定尤對背光相片的處理更得宜，外媒就找到了幾張據說為 Pixel 4 實拍的背光照片，效果的確比系統自動合成的 HDR 相片為佳：<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3367937/org/ec6581771ac57d6fb57df1cea31ec531.png/zeykDJy_VAo3KMElaZt5qQThYD92ts7uIgFy6CIBcug?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3367937%2Forg%2Fec6581771ac57d6fb57df1cea31ec531.png%2FzeykDJy_VAo3KMElaZt5qQThYD92ts7uIgFy6CIBcug%3Fv%3Dw800&h=e65a35e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3367975/org/18ac0dc33dc480766f35de69f0b0bff6.png/RE2_9jUzJfNK2b_ImZ96TnYodIqKvY9rSDcSf0g3En8?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3367975%2Forg%2F18ac0dc33dc480766f35de69f0b0bff6.png%2FRE2_9jUzJfNK2b_ImZ96TnYodIqKvY9rSDcSf0g3En8%3Fv%3Dw800&h=57ff8376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3367977/org/f6b5050470e8f966d31d28d42c6fd1c6.png/8YGmc5GmJIWIvTnITNqBZbIht4pXhp1tweoPW8HqD1s?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3367977%2Forg%2Ff6b5050470e8f966d31d28d42c6fd1c6.png%2F8YGmc5GmJIWIvTnITNqBZbIht4pXhp1tweoPW8HqD1s%3Fv%3Dw800&h=06efc57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3367976/org/3abba481219e38fe88df09d8860fe663.png/C5fBpeKsri1iTnKIOM5jDhGgSBWSgTH4IOpl8yDqZfM?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3367976%2Forg%2F3abba481219e38fe88df09d8860fe663.png%2FC5fBpeKsri1iTnKIOM5jDhGgSBWSgTH4IOpl8yDqZfM%3Fv%3Dw800&h=a71e6d81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce0ae4ce642fd43700fa29691f1d8d6f6e0b28d","tid":1622700,"uid":94828,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"係咪對靚有咩誤會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a090d592e7e2ffe55625852c8ff3e667c9626d","tid":1622700,"uid":43724,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"最last 個張真個人個邊發光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa27186db0e2b5283c08a57d3a2dccab28a7a0af","tid":1622700,"uid":123177,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"iPhone edit都做到<br />\n唔夠可以影埋raw🙃"},{"pid":"a2f2d708c9f8980f6d86e4f8d84d06da5a566249","tid":1622700,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"8ce0ae4ce642fd43700fa29691f1d8d6f6e0b28d","tid":1622700,"uid":94828,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"係咪對靚有咩誤會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:35:50.000Z","msg":"靚嘅標準人人唔同,可能你特別啲"},{"